        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Qiao Jing Jing, a well-known celebrity, finds herself in hot water when a leaked video of her terrible gaming skills threatens her endorsement deal. To save her reputation, she jumps into a gaming competition and decides to spend her free time getting better at the game. This leads her to reconnect with her old high school crush, Yu Tu, who’s now a brilliant aerospace engineer and a gaming pro. As he becomes\n\nher coach, the two start bonding over their shared passion, helping each other shine along the way.",
